data.description: ***PRICE ADJUSTMENT, SELLER IS SERIOUS!*** Welcome to an exclusive end unit offering in the highly sought after Fairway Knolls complex within the incredible Lake San Marcos community! This light and bright, spacious floor plan is nestled perfectly for the very best combination of convenience and privacy along with a lifestyle of tranquility and entertainment. • 2 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms • Views of Majestic Mountains and Breathtaking Sunsets • Desirable End Unit for Added Privacy • Spacious Living Areas with Abundant Natural Light Step outside to your private balcony and embrace the awe-inspiring views of the mountains and sunsets. Perfect for morning coffees or evening soirees, this outdoor space is an extension of the condo's charm. Indulge in the vibrant community life with access to a pristine golf course and serene lake with boating and fishing! Enjoy your evenings with a round of golf, a leisurely stroll around the water's edge or a delicious meal at Amalfi Cucina. This active community offers a plethora of activities ensuring there's always something for everyone. The condo comes with convenient covered parking, making your daily routine hassle-free. This condo is not just a home, it's a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to own a piece of paradise in this coveted golf course and lake community. Schedule a showing today and make this dream condo your reality!
